                        "displayName": "Gary Martellino",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "ZF-2387 Should be disregarded as it duplicates the issue in ZF-588.  The problem actually existed within the iconv extentions implementation across a couple servers in our organization.  Sorry for the confusion.  ",
