                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Gary, could I ask you to attach generated PDF to the issue? It may help a lot.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-02-01T10:29:00.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-02-01T10:29:00.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/18785",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gmartellino",
                        "name": "gmartellino",
                        "displayName": "Gary Martellino",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hi Alexander, the problem actually had to do with the iconv extension in our PHP installation.  Being that the character encoding was not found, it silently dropped all the characters it was trying to draw using drawText().  The framework method works as its supposed to and there is no actual issue.  Once I found that our iconv was at fault everything came together.  Thank you for your response.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gmartellino",
                        "name": "gmartellino",
                        "displayName": "Gary Martellino",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-02-01T11:59:32.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-02-01T11:59:32.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/18791",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alexander",
                        "name": "alexander",
                        "displayName": "Alexander Veremyev",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Good!\nI think that may be a common problem for Zend_Pdf and other ZF components and should be mentioned somewhere in the documentation... Thanks for the info!",
